import React from "react";
import { Typography, Box, Grid, Card, CardContent, Button } from "@mui/material";

function Dashboard() {
  return (
    <Box>
      <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom component="h1">
        Benvenuto nella Dashboard
      </Typography>
      <Grid container spacing={3}>
        {/* Scheda 1 */}
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
          <Card raised> {/* raised aggiunge un'ombra per profondità */}
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h5" component="div" gutterBottom>
                Riepilogo Dati
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                Qui puoi visualizzare un riepilogo rapido delle informazioni più importanti.
              </Typography>
              <Button variant="contained" color="primary" sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
                Vedi Dettagli
              </Button>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        {/* Scheda 2 */}
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h5" component="div" gutterBottom>
                Impostazioni Veloci
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                Accedi rapidamente alle tue impostazioni preferite.
              </Typography>
              <Button variant="outlined" color="secondary" sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
                Modifica Impostazioni
              </Button>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        {/* Scheda 3 */}
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h5" component="div" gutterBottom>
                Notifiche Recenti
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                Controlla le ultime notifiche e avvisi.
              </Typography>
              <Button variant="text" color="info" sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
                Visualizza Tutte
              </Button>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default Dashboard;
